snippet.title: SPIDER DISCO - [full gameplay] (SPOILERS!!!)
snippet.description:
A short indie game about a drone that grew up with spiders.
Made for gamejam called GryfJam 2017 with Sebastian Krzyszkowiak.
Play here for free: https://holypangolin.itch.io/spider-disco

Bobby humbly asks you to like and subscribe! Thank you!

Follow us on Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/holypangolin/
